      "name": "Experimental hemolysis index comparison — FDA pump benchmark",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against FDA benchmark experimental data at 2500 RPM and 5 L/min. Relative error 8.3%, within the 15% acceptance band. No uncertainty quantification was performed on this comparison; scatter in experimental replicates was noted but not formally propagated.",
