      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pressure-head validation across operating envelope",
      "description": "Simulated pressure rise across five flow-speed operating points compared to published experimental data. Mean absolute error 4.7 mmHg. Acceptance criterion: MAE < 10 mmHg. Criterion met. No formal uncertainty quantification applied to pressure boundary conditions or turbulence model parameters.",
